This is the Guide to help operate MyFoodApp.
The app is made up of three types of Time scheduled meals which are Morning, Afternoon, Night and also Dessert.
When you want a Morning Meal, you shall type "Morning" and then press the "Submit" button then the app will automatically suggest a Meal for that Specific time.
When you want an Afternoon Meal, you shall type "Afternoon" and then press the "Submit" button then the app will automatically suggest a Meal for that specific time.
When you want a Night Meal, you shall type "Night" and then press the "Submit" button then the app will automatically suggest a meal for that specific time.
When you want a Dessert, you shall type "Dessert" and then press the Submit" button then the app will automatically suggest a Dessert for you.
Thank You.
